68
00:04:22,769 --> 00:04:23,899
Aku hendak meminta maaf.

69
00:04:23,899 --> 00:04:25,269
Alih-alih pergi ke sana
dengan tangan kosong dan bilang,

70
00:04:25,269 --> 00:04:26,944
"Maaf, Sanchez",

71
